# Scout Activities Platform

This is a Next.js 15 application for scout leaders to browse activities, build programs, and manage content. The platform supports Portuguese (PT) and English (EN) localization with URL-based routing.

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: Next.js 15 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui
- **Backend**: PostgreSQL, Drizzle ORM, Auth.js
- **Testing**: Vitest, Playwright
- **Documentation**: OpenAPI/Swagger

## Key Features
- Activity browsing with search and filtering
- Program builder with drag & drop
- Export functionality (Excel/PDF)
- Rating and commenting system
- Public program templates
- Admin content management
- Internationalization (PT/EN)
- Google OAuth with domain restriction
